onderful chemical reactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every round was a new version that had never been seen before, and the rich Roguelike elements would make you never tired of playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 + 1 &gt; 2? 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 +... Of course it was infinite!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726870/extras/image3.gif?t=1738921505\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2726870/extras/4-en.png?t=1738921505\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>62 distinctive Vehicles</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>20 main bases with with different features</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>100+ unique Super Modules</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dozens of mysterious objects that reverse the situation</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Several different styles and interesting bosses, <i>Mummy Chick, Brood Queen, MagiBat</i>... Explore their unique mechanisms to the fullest</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>More modes - [<i>Random Endless</i>] mode is now officially released, and you can compete with other players. Our leaderboard will show the highest scores of players around the world. Come and create your own strongest vehicle system and become a true Loop Master!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Loop Recruit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2726870/bda57749b82652bd1e9b10e3e66ab267a3620c25.jpg"},{"name":"Loop Lieutenant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2726870/01b1bd5929bfbde3d01d